---
title: Apricot-Glazed Chicken with Thyme-Roasted Potatoes and Carrots
description: Crispy-skinned chicken is delicious enough on its own, but we’re upping the ante even further with a sweet-and-spicy apricot glaze. A touch of chili flakes on these carrots gives them an unexpected zing. If you’re not keen on spice, simply scale back the chili flakes.
